1. *Porota* je jednoglasno odlučila da je optuženi kriv. (The jury unanimously decided that the defendant is guilty.)
2. Advokat je uložio prigovor na sastav *porote*. (The lawyer objected to the composition of the jury.)
3. Članovi *porote* su bili pozvani da prisustvuju suđenju. (The jury members were summoned to attend the trial.)
4. Sudija je prozvao imena članova *porote*. (The judge called out the names of the jury members.)
5. *Porotnik* je izrazio svoje mišljenje o slučaju. (The juror expressed his opinion about the case.)
6. Optuženi je zatražio da bude suđeno pred *porotom*. (The defendant requested to be tried by a jury.)
7. Članovi *porote* su bili smješteni u hotelskoj sobi tokom suđenja. (The jury members were housed in a hotel room during the trial.)
8. Advokat je ispitivao svjedoka pred *porotom*. (The lawyer examined a witness before the jury.)
9. Nakon nekoliko sati razmatranja dokaza, *porota* je donijela presudu. (After several hours of deliberation, the jury reached a verdict.)
10. Sudija je pozvao *porotnika* da pročita presudu. (The judge asked the juror to read the verdict.)